---
// Landing A/B selector — plain HTML, no layout
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Otwarty Sklep — A/B</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .c { max-width: 400px; }
  .logo {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  a {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #000;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  a:hover { background: #000; color: #fff; }
  a span { font-weight: 400; color: #888; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  a:hover span { color: #999; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="c">
  <div class="logo">Otwarty Sklep</div>
  <h1>A/B Test</h1>
  <p>Dwie wersje landing page</p>
  <div class="links">
    <a href="/landing/a/">Mam sklep, chcę AI <span>Wariant A</span></a>
    <a href="/landing/b/">Chcę sprzedawać przez AI <span>Wariant B</span></a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
